  "texts": [
    "It is carried out on a Windows system equipped with an TITAN NVIDIA Xt GPU.",
    "It attains an accuracies of 65.35%, 86.36%, and 94.82% for distinguishing sMCI from NC, AD from NC, pMCI from NC.",
    "Finally, Raju et al. (2021) devised a technique for multilevel classification of AD using DL.",
    "The datasets are categorized as ND, VMD, MID, and MOD.",
    "It employs TL with VGG16 using fastai."
